c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Surfer and Zimmwriter share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Seo Tools. Where Surfer pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Multilingual and Api Access and Team Collaboration and Browser Extension, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Zimmwriter uniquely offers Templates, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Surfer holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Zimmwriter scores 7/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Zimmwriter comes in at a lower starting price of $14/mo, while Surfer begins at $89/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
